omacy, with our actions thus drastically reducing the number of rash actions that our human nature would normally dictate. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utwotribes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Twotribes</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/29/01 5:00:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=78.topic&index=7>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Ending World War II</span><hr size=1> In my opinion it is only a matter of time before  a terrorist network detonates one in a major city. Unless we can effectively hamstring the World access of these groups.<br><br>So long as Nations support, train, finance and encourage Terrorism this remains a REAL threat.<br><br>We are fortunate that none have been used before now, the collapse of the Soviet Union has placed the possibility of weapons of this sort in one form or another being accessed by Terrorists. The Government in Russia and the countries formed by the demise of the Soviet Union that have these weapons (Ukriane for one) have a poor history of paying and supporting their military and security forces.<br><br>I seriously DOUBT that if the current network had one and the means to get it into a major city they would even think twice about using it.<br><br>MAD, Mutally Assured Destruction only works when you have a clearly defined target to assure destruction against. Missile defense needs to be (IMO) developed and deployed world wide. Though this wont stop the use of a nuclear bomb due to manpack sized ones, it will prevent a rogue Nation from threatening anyone.<br><br>The people that are waging the terrorist war against us DO NOT care about human life. It is simple, if you dont submit to the will of this organization , they feel you do not deserve to live. <br><br>The only country that has a functioning anti missile defense is Russia. According to the treaty each of us were allowed to deploy one such system around one target. Of course at the time of the agreement the Soviets had the only WORKING system, ours showed promise but was scuttled and abandoned due to the treaty (in the 70's). No working system was made by the Reagan era research, though some promising technology has come from it. And that research continues.<br><br>I find it hard to understand a mind set that THINKS dismantling a weapons system or military structure will encourage the SAME in the bigots, racists and petty despots that dream of global power. They understand only one thing... Force. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uwallaceoffv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>WallaceofFV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/29/01 5:22:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=78.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Ending World War II</span><hr size=1> We all should just enjoy ourselves while we can. Our government is full of pansies. We lack the consensus to exert the FORCE needed to stop these maniacs. We might as well just hand Israel over to the PLO, close our borders and hide in our basements for 10 years. Maybe if we keep our heads in the sand long enough it will go away.<br><br>(And for those who think bombing Afganistan